  <div id="text-content_95F021E0-094A-0135-9DA0-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>The first few times you create a new course in Canvas, it's a challenge to remember all of the steps required. The Course Setup Checklist exists to help you remember to cover all your bases before the course goes live.</p>
<p><strong>Note</strong>: If your course does not include a Setup Checklist, your institution has enabled the Canvas course setup tutorial instead, which displays in the Course Home Page and each index page in Course Navigation.</p>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_course_setup_checklist" data-step-uuid="904f2b3d-7a64-40b9-b58d-c9f672da5884">
    <h2 id="open_course_setup_checklist" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Course Setup Checklist</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/120/508/original/364782fb-685c-4ae2-9c83-876f30ae2f50.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
